    <name>Key Idea: Distance learning can support inclusive communities of learning.​</name>
    <intro>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{671f52c5-617a-487f-bdbb-f4fd2f02621e}{238}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{671f52c5-617a-487f-bdbb-f4fd2f02621e}{238}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/Key%20Idea.png" alt="" width="140" height="136" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_middle"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{671f52c5-617a-487f-bdbb-f4fd2f02621e}{238}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Distance learning is&amp;nbsp;when you and your students are separated by physical distance and use a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;variety of media and technologies to communicate, teach, and learn.&amp;nbsp;When done well, distance learning&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;can address a number of challenges that could prevent learners from persisting in their education as&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;adult learners. These challenges include non-academic factors such as a lack of reliable transportation, access&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;to childcare, or the demands of busy lives.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{671f52c5-617a-487f-bdbb-f4fd2f02621e}{241}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;With distance learning, students can learn whenever and wherever it makes the most sense to them while still&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;receiving an equally rigorous education to their peers who take in-person courses,&amp;nbsp;but only if&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;the learning has been carefully designed to address social and emotional needs and accessibility &lt;a href="$@PAGEVIEWBYID*9888@$" target="_blank"&gt;(Cochran &amp;amp; Brown, 2016)&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/divider%20wave.png" alt="" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
